OL,3,CTravel compensation and penalties:
OL,4,CWhat are your rights amid global IT
OL,5,Coutage?
OL,7,FAn unprecedented wave of global IT
OL,8,Fissues have overwhelmed travel and
OL,9,Fother essential services.
OL,11,FTravellers around the world are facing
OL,12,Fgrounded flights and delayed trains,
OL,13,Fcausing widespread frustration and
OL,14,Fchaos.
OL,16,FThe technology difficulties have also
OL,17,Fdisrupted some payment systems,
OL,18,Fleaving consumers unable to make
OL,19,Ftransactions.
