OL,3,CTravel compensation and penalties:
OL,4,CWhat are your rights amid global IT
OL,5,Coutage?
OL,7,FThe airline or trainline you are
OL,8,Ftravelling on is the first point of
OL,9,Fcall for updates on their individual
OL,10,Fpolicy.
OL,12,FRory Boland, Editor of Which? Travel,
OL,13,Fsaid compensation for delayed or
OL,14,Fcancelled flights "will not be
OL,15,Fpayable" as these are "extraordinary
OL,16,Fcircumstances".
OL,18,FBut, he added, "airlines nonetheless
OL,19,Fhave a duty to look after you,
OL,20,Fincluding providing meals and
OL,21,Faccommodation if it becomes necessary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
