OL,7,F"They should also reroute you as
OL,8,Fquickly as possible, though given the
OL,9,Fglobal nature of the problem, this may
OL,10,Fnot be immediately possible."
OL,12,FIt is similar for trains, with refunds
OL,13,Fand compensation unlikely if the issue
OL,14,Fwas unavoidable and not the company's
OL,15,Ffault.
