OL,4,CWhat are your rights amid global IT
OL,5,Coutage?
OL,7,FWith evidence, it may be possible to
OL,8,Fget the costs covered by the bank.
OL,10,F"If the bank rejects your request for
OL,11,Fcompensation, make a complaint to the
OL,12,Fbank. If that's rejected, you can go
OL,13,Fto the Financial Ombudsman Service,
OL,14,Fwhich is free and can force the bank
OL,15,Fto pay you compensation."
