OL,3,CTravel compensation and penalties:
OL,4,CWhat are your rights amid global IT
OL,5,Coutage?
OL,7,FFraudsters are known to take advantage
OL,8,Fof the confusion in outages like
OL,9,Fthese, particularly as banks navigate
OL,10,Fthe impact to services.
OL,12,FMr Richardson said: "I'd be extremely
OL,13,Fsuspicious of anyone who gets in
OL,14,Fcontact with you out of the blue,
OL,15,Fpretending to be from your bank. I
OL,16,Fwould actually advise putting phone
OL,17,Fdown on them and potentially
OL,18,Fcontacting your bank directly.
